Notes: First round of the 2005 ECAC South Region Tournament.
Senior Holly Liebl scores a career-high 26 points and records her 12th
double-double of the season to lead Desales past Grove City and into the
Final Four of the ECAC South Region Tournament Championship.
Game.Officials: Jim Hollister,  Bill Gross,  Phil Wingert
